B) I re-read this thread from the top to bottem, and not a single post made any sort of dirogatory remark towards Submina in any way, shape or form.  The closest thing I can see to any sort of &quot;jumping on her&quot; is in my post where I commented that after spending time doing &quot;pure NBG&quot; raids in the company of a good guild, the more FFA way of handling loot that is common in pickup raids might be disgusting.  My goal in that statement was actually to COMPLIMENT her and her guild for the way they handle loot.  The worst part of Dragon raids is the loot whining that goes on.  I hate it, and don't stand for it on my raids.<br>
